FBIS4-68013 "jptot018__l94059" JPRS-TOT-94-018-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 28 April 1994 WEST EUROPE SPAIN `Sought After' ETA Terrorist Arrested in Barcelona `Sought After' ETA Terrorist Arrested in Barcelona LD2804201394 Madrid TVE Internacional Television in Spanish 1900 GMT 28 Apr 94 LD2804201394 Madrid TVE Internacional Television Spanish BFN [Excerpts] Felipe San Epifanio, one of the most sought after Basque Fatherland and Liberty [ETA] terrorists in recent months, was arrested at 1500 in a bar in the Olympic marina in Barcelona. The terrorist was armed and resisted arrest. [passage omitted] After the arrest of Felipe San Epifanio, aka Pipe, three other suspected terrorists linked with the attacks perpetrated in Barcelona in recent months are being sought by the police. They are Gregorio Vicario Setien, Rosario Ezkerra Perez de Nanclares, and Dulos Lopez Resines.
